### Function Description

query job link by gse task id

### Request Parameters

#### Interface parameters

| Fields      | Type | Required | Description |
|-------------|------|----------|-------------|
| gse_task_id | Int  | yes      | gse task id |

### Example of request

- GET

```json
/api/v3/system/query_job_instance?gse_task_id=a: aa: aa: a
```

### Example of response

```json
{
    "result": true,
    "code": 0,
    "data": {
        "bk_scope_type": "biz",
        "bk_scope_id": "1",
        "job_instance_id": 1000000,
        "step_instance_id": 10000001,
        "retry_count": 0,
        "batch": 1,
        "gse_task_id": "aa:aa:aa:aa",
        "link": [
            "https://xxx.com"
        ]
    },
    "job_request_id": "xxx"
}
```

